Package io.sphere.sdk.types.commands.updateactions

Provides the possible operations which can be performed on update commands for types.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddEnumValue
    Adds an a new EnumValue value to an EnumFieldType field.
    AddFieldDefinition
    Adds another field definition to a Type (NOT ProductType).
    AddLocalizedEnumValue
    Adds an a new LocalizedEnumValue value to an LocalizedEnumFieldType field.
    ChangeEnumValueOrder
    This action changes the order of enum values in an EnumType field definition.
    ChangeFieldDefinitionLabel
    Changes the label.
    ChangeFieldDefinitionOrder
    Changes the order of the fields.
    ChangeKey
    Changes the key of a Type.
    ChangeLocalizedEnumValueOrder
    This action changes the order of localized enum values in a LocalizedEnumType field definition.
    ChangeName
    Changes the name of the type.
    RemoveFieldDefinition
    Removes a field definition from a type.
    SetDescription
    Changes the description of the type.

Package io.sphere.sdk.types.commands.updateactions Description

Provides the possible operations which can be performed on update commands for types.
